Method Purpose Use Case <code>execute_script()</code> Execute multi-line scripts Complex logic, DOM manipulation <code>evaluate()</code> Evaluate expressions Quick property access, calculations <pre><code># execute_script - for statements and logic
result = driver.execute_script("""
    if (document.querySelector('h1')) {
        return document.querySelector('h1').textContent;
    }
    return null;
""")

# evaluate - for expressions
result = driver.evaluate("document.querySelector('h1')?.textContent")
</code></pre>
